We’re delighted to announce the recent launch of The Counter Ruck, our new weekly rugby newsletter. Sign up to get the view from the press box from our correspondent Gerry Thornley straight to your inbox every Friday. The newsletter contains exclusive content from you won’t find anywhere else on The Irish Times as well as a selection of our best rugby articles during the week. To receive the email, sign up using the widget at the top of this article or on our newsletters page. In the latest edition of the newsletter, Gerry takes the temperature in the French camp ahead of Ireland’s crunch clash with the Six Nations holders in Dublin.